OL,6,G1900FUniversity Challenge
OL,7,     GThe second round continues, with
OL,8,     Gtwo more teams of students eager
OL,9,     Gto snatch a second win and the
OL,10,     Gplace in the quarter-finals that
OL,11,     Ggoes with it. Jeremy Paxman asks
OL,12,     Gthe questions.
OL,13,G1930FOnly Connect
OL,14,     GQuiz show in which connections
OL,15,     Gmust be made between seemingly
OL,16,     Gunconnected things. Three chess
OL,17,     Gplayers take on a team who write
OL,18,     Gpuzzles for charity.
